quran[27]{c,v,t}:
  10,26,LILLEDHINE ‘EHSENUL-HUSNA WE ZIJADETUN WE LA JERHEKU WUXHUHEHUM KATERUN WE LA DHILLETUN ‘ULA’IKE ‘ESHABUL-XHENNETI HUM FIHA HALIDUNE
  10,27,WEL-LEDHINE KESEBU ES-SEJJI’ATI XHEZA’U SEJJI’ETIN BIMITHLIHA WE TERHEKUHUM DHILLETUN MA LEHUM MINEL-LAHI MIN ‘ASIMIN KE’ENNEMA ‘UGSHIJET WUXHUHUHUM KITA’ÆN MINEL-LEJLI MUDHLIMÆN ‘ULA’IKE ‘ESHABU EN-NARI HUM FIHA HALIDUNE
  10,28,WE JEWME NEHSHURUHUM XHEMI’ÆN THUMME NEKULU LILLEDHINE ‘ESHREKU MEKANEKUM ‘ENTUM WE SHUREKA’UUKUM FEZEJJELNA BEJNEHUM WE KALE SHUREKA’UUHUM MA KUNTUM ‘IJANA TA’BUDUNE
  10,29,FEKEFA BILLAHI SHEHIDÆN BEJNENA WE BEJNEKUM ‘IN KUNNA ‘AN ‘IBADETIKUM LEGAFILINE
  10,30,HUNALIKE TEBLU KULLU NEFSIN MA ‘ESLEFET WE RUDDU ‘ILA ELLAHI MEWLAHUMUL-HEKKI WE DELLE ‘ANHUM MA KANU JEFTERUNE
  10,31,KUL MEN JERZUKUKUM MINE ES-SEMA’I WEL-’ERDI ‘EMMEN JEMLIKU ES-SEM’A WEL-’EBSARE WE MEN JUHRIXHUL-HEJJE MINEL-MEJJITI WE JUHRIXHUL-MEJJITE MINEL-HEJJI WE MEN JUDEBBIRUL-’EMRE FESEJEKULUNEL-LAHU FEKUL ‘EFELA TETTEKUNE
  10,32,FEDHELIKUMU ELLAHU REBBUKUMUL-HEKKU FEMADHA BA’DEL-HEKKI ‘ILLA ED-DELALU FE’ENNA TUSREFUNE
  10,33,KEDHALIKE HEKKAT KELIMETU RABBIKE ‘ALEL-LEDHINE FESEKU ‘ENNEHUM LA JU’UMINUNE
  10,34,KUL HEL MIN SHUREKA’IKUM MEN JEBDE’UL-HALKA THUMME JU’IDUHU KULI ELLAHU JEBDE’UL-HALKA THUMME JU’IDUHU FE’ENNA TU’UFEKUNE
  10,35,KUL HEL MIN SHUREKA’IKUM MEN JEHDI ‘ILAL-HEKKI KULI ELLAHU JEHDI LILHEKKI ‘EFEMEN JEHDI ‘ILAL-HEKKI ‘EHEKKU ‘EN JUTTEBE’A ‘EMMEN LA JEHIDDI ‘ILLA ‘EN JUHDA FEMA LEKUM KEJFE TEHKUMUNE
  10,36,WE MA JETTEBI’U ‘EKTHERUHUM ‘ILLA DHENNÆN ‘INNE EDH-DHENNE LA JUGNI MINEL-HEKKI SHEJ’ÆN ‘INNALL-LLAHE ‘ALIMUN BIMA JEF’ALUNE
  10,37,WE MA KANE HADHAL-KUR’ANU ‘EN JUFTERA MIN DUNI ELLAHI WE LEKIN TESDIKAL-LEDHI BEJNE JEDEJHI WE TEFSILEL-KITABI LA REJBE FIHI MIN RABBIL-’ALEMINE
  10,38,‘EM JEKULUNE EFTERAHU KUL FE’TU BISURETIN MITHLIHI WE ED’U MENI ESTETA’TUM MIN DUNI ELLAHI ‘IN KUNTUM SADIKINE
  10,39,BEL KEDHDHEBU BIMA LEM JUHITU BI’ILMIHI WE LEMMA JE’TIHIM TE’WILUHU KEDHALIKE KEDHDHEBEL-LEDHINE MIN KABLIHIM FANDHUR KEJFE KANE ‘AKIBETU EDH-DHALIMINE
  10,40,WE MINHUM MEN JU’UMINU BIHI WE MINHUM MEN LA JU’UMINU BIHI WE REBBUKE ‘A’LEMU BIL-MUFSIDINE
  10,41,WE ‘IN KEDHDHEBUKE FEKUL LI ‘AMELI WE LEKUM ‘AMELUKUM ‘ENTUM BERI’UNE MIMMA ‘A’MELU WE ‘ENA BERI’UN MIMMA TA’MELUNE
  10,42,WE MINHUM MEN JESTEMI’UNE ‘ILEJKE ‘EFE’ENTE TUSMI’U ES-SUMME WE LEW KANU LA JA’KILUNE
  10,43,WE MINHUM MEN JENDHURU ‘ILEJKE ‘EFE’ENTE TEHDIL-’UMJE WE LEW KANU LA JUBSIRUNE
  10,44,‘INNALL-LLAHE LA JEDHLIMU EN-NASE SHEJ’ÆN WE LEKINNE EN-NASE ‘ENFUSEHUM JEDHLIMUNE
  10,45,WE JEWME JEHSHURUHUM KE’EN LEM JELBETHU ‘ILLA SA’ATEN MINE EN-NEHARI JETA’AREFUNE BEJNEHUM KAD HASIREL-LEDHINE KEDHDHEBU BILIKA’I ELLAHI WE MA KANU MUHTEDINE
  10,46,WE ‘IMMA NURIJENNEKE BA’DEL-LEDHI NA’IDUHUM ‘EW NETEWEFFEJENNEKE FE’ILEJNA MERXHI’UHUM THUMMEL-LAHU SHEHIDUN ‘ALA MA JEF’ALUNE
  10,47,WE LIKULLI ‘UMMETIN RESULUN FE’IDHA XHA’E RESULUHUM KUDIJE BEJNEHUM BIL-KISTI WE HUM LA JUDHLEMUNE
  10,48,WE JEKULUNE META HADHAL-WA’DU ‘IN KUNTUM SADIKINE
  10,49,KUL LA ‘EMLIKU LINEFSI DERRÆN WE LA NEF’ÆN ‘ILLA MA SHA’EL-LAHU LIKULLI ‘UMMETIN ‘EXHELUN ‘IDHA XHA’E ‘EXHELUHUM FELA JESTE’HIRUNE SA’ATEN WE LA JESTEKDIMUNE
  10,50,KUL ‘ERE’EJTUM ‘IN ‘ETAKUM ‘ADHABUHU BEJATÆN ‘EW NEHARÆN MADHA JESTA’XHILU MINHUL-MUXHRIMUNE
  10,51,‘ETHUMME ‘IDHA MA WEKA’A ‘AMENTUM BIHI ‘AL’ANE WE KAD KUNTUM BIHI TESTA’XHILUNE
  10,52,THUMME KILE LILLEDHINE DHELEMU DHUKU ‘ADHABEL-HULDI HEL TUXHZEWNE ‘ILLA BIMA KUNTUM TEKSIBUNE